snippet.title: Stellaris - Humanoids Species Pack: Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Get it now: http://pdxint.at/2zNIR3g
Paradox Interactive, a publisher and developer of games that
tell human interest stories, today released a new Species Pack for Stellaris, the sci-fi grand strategy game from Paradox Development Studio. “Humanoids Species Pack,” available today on Windows, Mac, and Linux PCs, includes a wealth of new cosmetic content for ambitious galactic rulers. With new species portraits, ship models, music tracks, and voice sets for VIR, The Humanoids Species Pack provides more variety and character to Stellaris’ most-played phenotype, inspired by the classics of Western science fiction.
